years, the number of knights stationed here has grown, and so too has the
multitude of support personnel necessary.  Some knights have brought their
families to live here with them, and with that came a boom in population.  Now
there are many civilians living in Vingaard Keep, and this is where they go to
do their daily shopping.  It is an open-air market, which allows many
out-of-town vendors to come here and set up shop, selling their goods to the
locals before moving on.  The keep itself rises up to your north, and the
marketplace lies in all other directions from here.    
